@SenSanders We're Canadian. Our son fell ill with a rare disease at 2. It took several days in hospital to diagnose &amp; treat.

Total cost to our family: Parking and a bit of hospital food (for me.) That's it.

Not worrying about medical bills allowed us to focus 100% on our son's health.

On Monday, The Young Turks will start at 6pm ET and will stream @SenSanders town hall on #climatechange at 7pm ET. Watch at https://t.co/SAq3iYssvt.

@cenkuygur, @johniadarola, and @franifio will provide post town hall analysis on #tytlive for members.

